<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed my-4 text-base" style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif">The Heaven Designs process emphasizes accuracy, completeness, and regulatory compliance from the start. Integrated design teams ensure coordination between electrical, structural, and civil disciplines, eliminating the inconsistencies common with multi-vendor approaches. Rigorous quality assurance processes include multi-level reviews, standardized checklists, and compliance verification before any documentation reaches clients.</p>
